SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*), sum(p.gtp_losbaar_1+p.gtp_losbaar_2) from posities_gts p where p.gtp_be_volgnummer = ~1 and p.gtp_relatienummer <> 0 and p.gtp_rekeningsoort between 100 and 999
